{
  "texts": [
    "The BIOES scheme adopts E (end) to indicate the last character of an entity and represents the single-character entity using S (single); the other tokens are labeled as in the BIO tag scheme.",
    "In this study, the BIO tag scheme is adopted to label tokens.",
    "MethodologyIn this section, we describe the proposed multitask learningbased BCNN-CWS model in detail.",
    "Deep learning methods can automatically learn contextual information and thus perform well in NER tasks.",
    "However, a deep-learning-based NER system may not achieve a satisfactory performance if its hidden representations cannot be learned adequately, which frequently occurs in lowresource scenarios."
  ]
}